{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Util/ProfilerServer.html#Lean.Firefox.Profile.serve\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Firefox</span>.<span class=\"name\">Profile</span>.<span class=\"name\">serve</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">profile</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/System/IO.html#IO\">IO</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Serve the JSON-encoded `profile` over HTTP on an ephemeral `127.0.0.1` port and open it in the\nuser's default browser via `https://profiler.firefox.com`. Shuts down once the profile has been\nfetched (reloads inside the viewer are not supported); the user can also Ctrl+C as usual.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Util/ProfilerServer.html#Lean.Firefox.Profile.serve","kind":"def","line":42,"name":"Lean.Firefox.Profile.serve","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Util/ProfilerServer.lean#L42-L71"}}],"imports":["Init.System.IO","Init.System.Platform","Lean.Util.Profiler","Std.Http"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Util.ProfilerServer"}